headline: GTA Online
subtitle: F. CLINTON & PARTNER
content:
To get started with The Contract, partner with Franklin by investing in a state-of-the-art, multi-floor Agency available from Dynasty 8 Executive.

Business up front, optional armory, and vehicle workshop in the back. Just remember, “Celebrity Solutions” in Los Santos is more than security escorts and recoveries. Sometimes, it’s infiltration, espionage, and assassination.
